      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOT WORK (7) is yet to break through in nine starts but has run a number of placings. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing sixth (24.41) at this track. Can bounce back. ASPEN RIDGE (8) last start finished 4th over 388m at Gosford beaten 6 lengths (22.81) behind Stilton Sparkle in a Maiden on March 31. Looks one of the chances. MIA PARTY GIRL (1) settled well back early on debut and always towards the tail to finish eighth (23.76) at this track over 400m. Gets the coveted rails draw for the first time. Can do far better this time. SERGEANT DUKER (5) is a Jennifer Oates-trained newcomer by Koblenz out of Mighty Mrs. Start all important. Can run a bold race on debut.",
